          <div class="date-outer">
        
<h2 class='date-header'><span>Thursday, February 16, 2023</span></h2>

          <div class="date-posts">
        
<div class='post-outer'>
<div class='post hentry uncustomized-post-template' itemprop='blogPost' itemscope='itemscope' itemtype='http://schema.org/BlogPosting'>
<meta content='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYEqofNn55v8P6tTGRESvnisOjgf-xV__f58iTkGb3koALitbwDOW3_X0EAIcwLaS-wf3Sld09YvlHc_efi1dx4b4TeGpfml7FdZvK2VkRBNoy8vX87rJF44VTQPaEkNgf6mlPbG4FqO7rW9jEhEhssfLHbdlM_ABrg92mjMwKAGIw-I-19a0io9vQzw/w640-h360/thumbnail.jpg' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='1061568887130403538' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='218335595503952030' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='218335595503952030'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://vnd-peru.blogspot.com/2023/02/estudios-agrarios-brasil-luta-camponesa.html'>ESTUDIOS AGRARIOS BRASIL: Luta camponesa no Brasil e no México recebe solidariedade de ativistas da Europa</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-218335595503952030' itemprop='description articleBody'>
