 red;"><span style="color: #ffa400;"><br /></span></span></div><div style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;"><div class="yiv0915361141gmail_default" style="font-family: georgia, serif; font-size: small;"><span style="background-color: red;"><span style="color: #ffa400;">Fonte.&nbsp; AND</span></span></div><span style="color: #ffa400; font-size: x-large;"><a href="https://anovademocracia.com.br/ba-no-vale-do-jequirica-250-familias-camponesas-ocupam-latifundio/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" style="background-color: red;" target="_blank">BA: No Vale do Jequiriçá, 250 famílias camponesas ocupam latifúndio</a></span></div><div style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;"><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj4N4GhP389AIcrJbdm27SLvvPgaUM5vIDOn32N4vWO5iQz55JeCeC0EELgyqFR1xwz5qpDTa2qDsbCUD5D0JVCbYZXxCONhx-8AvvcCGEbdBv9q83EXJuHqqK_IqomJzdgcf5OMW2K9JZsvxoZrftuR6wEMC1liw6sqDHRGhwoNw60iLy0aISyunBVgA/s647/thumbnail%20(2).jpg" imageanchor="1" style="background-color: red; margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><span style="color: #ffa400;"><img border="0" data-original-height="485" data-original-width="647" height="480" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj4N4GhP389AIcrJbdm27SLvvPgaUM5vIDOn32N4vWO5iQz55JeCeC0EELgyqFR1xwz5qpDTa2qDsbCUD5D0JVCbYZXxCONhx-8AvvcCGEbdBv9q83EXJuHqqK_IqomJzdgcf5OMW2K9JZsvxoZrftuR6wEMC1liw6sqDHRGhwoNw60iLy0aISyunBVgA/w640-h480/thumbnail%20(2).jpg" width="640" /></span></a></div><span style="background-color: red;"><span style="color: #ffa400;"><br /></span></span><div class="img-preview-wrapper"><span style="background-color: red;"><span style="color: #ffa400;"><br /></span></span><span class="img-dl-btn" style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; bac